<%- @text = capture do -%>
Dear <%= @user.member.nil? ? @user.email : @user.member.first_name %>,

Your account has been created.

Username: <%=h @user.email %>  
Password: <%=h @user.password %>
  
Never share your password with anybody!  If you ever lose your password, we will reset it for you, but we will never ask you for it.

The first time you log in, you will be asked to change this password.

Visit this url to activate your account:

<%=h @url %>

<%- end -%>